<subSubSection pageId="28" pageNumber="29" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="28.[136,1452,1293,1423]" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">Thallus saxicolus, parvus. Laciniae filiformes, subteretiusculae. Pseudocyphellae lineares. Soralia lateralia vel laminalia. Pycnidia non visa. Apothecia nulla. Acida usnicum, sekikaicum, hypoprotocetraricum et succinprotocetraricum continens.</emphasis>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
